******************************
*****
*****  PERL PROGRAMMING  *****
*****
******************************

For those using Linux, there is a script named "setup-perl-linux.sh" which will
download various Perl programming language related documentation to your computer.
It will require Subversion (SVN), Git and Hg (Mercurial) to be installed.


